<h3><strong>Openings</strong></h3>
<p>The opportunity to serve at the <em>Youth Spectacular</em> is open to  all young adults who meet the outlined criteria. Sixty (60) counselors  and 20 staff members are needed! Please submit your <a href="Documents/community-connections/bys/counselorapp.pdf">application</a> early.</p>
<h3><strong>Counselors </strong></h3>
<p>The <em>Boise Youth Spectacular</em> will accommodate 600-800 youth.  Youth are divided into groups of ten with one counselor assigned to each  group. The counselors spend all of their time with their groups and  report directly to their supervisor.</p>
<p><strong>Counselors are:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>to be with the youth throughout the conference</li>
<li>to provide supervision </li>
<li>to be an example and a friend. </li>
</ul>
<p>The effective counselor must be diligent and service oriented; he or  she must have a genuine desire to help the youth strengthen their  testimonies of Jesus Christ and their commitment to live the gospel.</p>
<p>Counselors must be at least eighteen (18) and high school graduates (2011) and no older than 35.</p>
<h3><strong>Staff</strong></h3>
<p>Staff members are heavily involved in administration of the myriad of duties that make the <em>Youth Spectacular</em> successful. Their duties include registration, food service, crowd control, assisting counselors, and much more.<br /> Staff members must be 18 to 35-years old.<br /> Meals and t-shirts will be provided for the staff.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" GroupStart=""><xPower Type="List" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><xpowercomponent_Optional Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="Facebook;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false" /></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" /><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" /><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" /></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="x35600" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" /><xPower Type="List" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" List="xpowercomponent_ContentSnippet"><xPower Type="Component" Name="ContentSnippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="ContentSnippet" /></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="